    <introduction>
      <para>Error XTT0001: At least one XSL transformation is required</para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Cause</title>
      <content>
        <para>This error occurs if no XSL transformation files are specified in
the <codeInline>XslTransform</codeInline> build task's
<codeInline>Transformations</codeInline> property.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Solution</title>
      <content>
        <para>Specify at least on XSL transformation in the
<codeInline>Transformations</codeInline> property so that the
<application>XslTransform</application> tool has something to use when
transforming the input file.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

